                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330103-180-off1024 t18330103-180-cd1025"></join>, 1 show-glass, value 2s. 6d., and 3 lbs. weight of sweetmeats, value 5s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18330103-180-victim1679" type="victimName">
